										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The crest clicks into place, floor hinges unlock, and the ring on the floor begins to spin.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Any companions step back, and the player looks around in positive anticipation.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The floor ring slowly rises up as the four pillars also rise, the crystals they're topped with starting to glow warmly as if suffused with sunlight.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The still-spinning floor ring aligns with the gyro, and as it also begins to move and rotate a glow forms at its core.  - The gyro aligns its rings into a flat horizontal plane over the mace.  -  A shaft of light coming down around mace, as the gyro glow fades and the mace’s glow intensifies.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The mace unlocks from its rigid upright position and begins floating in the shaft of light in a slanted, bobbing, “take me” manner.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The player gently takes the mace as the other glows fade slightly, admiring the mace’s pulsing glow as companions step forward." />
										</node>
